"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 513px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Benefit of accelerated t-PA in acute myocardial infarction",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 493px; height: 243px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The overall one-year mortality for patients treated with different thrombolytic strategies in the GUSTO-1 trial. The mortality rate was lower in patients treated with accelerated t-PA compared to those receiving streptokinase and either intravenous (IV) or subcutaneous (SQ) heparin (p = 0.003) or t-PA and streptokinase in combination (p = 0.05).",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Data from Califf RM, White HD, Van de Werk F, et al for the GUSTO-1 Investigators, Circulation 1996; 94:1233.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
